name: openquake.engine
raw_recipe:
{% set version = "3.1.0.post1" %}

package:
  name: openquake.engine
  version: {{ version }}

source:
  url: https://pypi.io/packages/source/o/openquake.engine/openquake.engine-{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: 65f3c26bac04aa30f5e95e03379c5930b4739d0074d8ba5cfc442118a850d8b6

build:
  noarch: python
  number: 0
  script: python -m pip install --no-deps --ignore-installed .

requirements:
  build:
    - python >=3
    - pip
  run:
    - python >=3
    - h5py >=2.5
    - numpy >=1.8
    - scipy >=0.13
    - pyzmq >=16.0
    - psutil >=3.2.0
    - shapely >=1.5.11
    - docutils >=0.12
    - decorator >=4.0.10
    - django >=1.10
    - matplotlib >=1.5
    - requests >=2.2
    - pyshp >=1.2.3
    - pyyaml
    - mock
